          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I place an order?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Browse our collection of organic matcha, loose leaf teas, superfood powders, and spices. Add your favorite products to your cart and proceed to checkout. Enter your shipping and payment details, and we'll take care of the rest. It's quick and easy!</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row-1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What payment methods do you accept?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>We accept major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express), PayPal, and other secure online payment platforms. All payment information is encrypted and secure for your protection.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you offer wholesale pricing?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! We offer wholesale pricing on our teas, matcha, spices, and superfood powders for businesses and bulk orders. Contact our team to discuss volume pricing and set up a wholesale account.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I track my order?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely! Once your order ships, we'll send you a tracking number via email. Use this number to monitor your package and see its estimated delivery date. If you have any tracking issues, our support team is here to help.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row-4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are your subscription boxes?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>We offer two subscription options: a Matcha Subscription Box ($49.99) and a Seasonal Subscription Box ($59.99) that deliver curated selections of our premium products regularly to your door. You can pause, skip, or cancel anytime.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row-5": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I contact customer support?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>We're here to help! Reach out through our contact form, and we'll respond within 24 hours on business days. Whether you have questions about products, orders, or need assistance, our team is ready to support you.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
