            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and strong odors. Keep matcha refrigerated after opening for optimal freshness. Reseal bags tightly after each use. Check individual product pages for specific storage recommendations.</p>",
